---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="HederaCon 2025 — AES" bodyClass="inner-page">

  <div class="container-fluid event-hero">
    <div class="event-hero-inner event-hero-inner--mid">
      <div class="event-hero-left">
        <div class="event-location">Denver, USA</div>
        <div class="event-title">HederaCon<br />2025</div>
        <div class="event-tagline">
          Hedera hosted a 1-day conference adjacent to ETH Denver in February 2025 catering to the developer crowd followed by a closing party at Meow Wolf.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-hero-right">
        <div class="event-detail-card">
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">About the Event</div>
            <p>We selected The Arch, a former brewery and warehouse that perfectly suited the needs of the event — and pushed the client outside of their comfort zone. The main stage featured three LED screens and a stunning LED board spanning the length of the room, creating a grand re-entry moment for Hedera. The closing party at Meow Wolf had attendees lining up for hours and staying until the bitter end.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid event-gallery">
    <div class="event-gallery-inner">
      <div class="gallery-grid gallery-grid--four">
        <div class="gallery-placeholder" style="background-image: url('/images/work3.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder" style="background-image: url('/images/work5.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder" style="background-image: url('/images/work7.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder" style="background-image: url('/images/work9.png')"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid event-back">
    <div class="event-back-inner">
      <a href="/work" class="cr-btn white ex-padding">← Back to All Events</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>
